title: Beauty video blogger Farah Dhukai shares her best DIY tricks | NT News
text:
-Skin glowing

And the simple DIY recipe that gets rid of split ends . 
You only need a ripe papaya (seeds removed), honey, almond oil and a plastic bag. Yep, it really is that simple. A post shared by Farah D (@farahdhukai) on Apr 11, 2016 at 5:04pm PDT 
Both videos have received millions of views, with thousands of people from around the world praising the beauty blogger. 
So if you love cheap natural skincare tips and beauty hacks, Farah Dhukai will probably become your new favourite person. The biggest beauty trends of 2016 0:56
